```
package main

import (
    "fmt"
    "strings"
    "github.com/google/uuid"
)

func main() {
    uuidWithHyphen := uuid.New()
    fmt.Println(uuidWithHyphen)
    uuid := strings.Replace(uuidWithHyphen.String(), "-", "", -1)
    fmt.Println(uuid)
}
```

```
package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"strings"

	"github.com/pborman/uuid"
)

func main() {
	uuidWithHyphen := uuid.NewRandom()
	fmt.Println(uuidWithHyphen)
	uuid := strings.Replace(uuidWithHyphen.String(), "-", "", -1)
	fmt.Println(uuid)
}
```
